{"type": "article", "id": 2958, "title": "BottleLoft冰箱小工具", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-21T08:20:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052324343YqDxXLawPGNuRpt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冰箱的冷藏室永远给人搁不下的感觉，而每一层搁架的顶部却总是有很大的利用空间。日前，Brian Conti 设计了一款名为“ BottleLoft ”的小工具，利用磁铁原理，可以将自己牢牢吸附于冰箱顶层，同时也能一次性吸附三瓶玻璃瓶装的饮料或是啤酒，吸力强大，不会担心容器会掉落，从而腾出了底层空间放置其它物品。目前，BottleLoft 正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/690647277/bottleloft-by-strong-like-bull-magnets\" target=\"_blank\">KICKSTARTER </a>进行众筹。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232432QqNpsGkezmICwOHn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052324320XmQ9JdOH7qWE6KR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232432hWoTAOVm7uiUQ4St.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232433zq9mlUbHGFe3AQsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232433fWR23xZSD05M8OG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}